      • contentType

        Connection.KeyVal contentType(String contentType)
        Set the Content Type header used in the MIME body (aka mimetype) when uploading files. Only useful if inputStream(InputStream) is set.

        Will default to application/octet-stream.

        参数:
        contentType - the new content type
        返回:
        this KeyVal
